<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.242958>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Leposternon bagual sp. nov. (holotype, FML 11319). (A) Dorsal, (B) lateral, (C) ventral view of the head; (D) pectoral and (E) cloacal regions. Scale bar = 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/242958/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.242959>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Leposternon bagual sp. nov. (holotype, FML 11319). (A) Dorsal, (B) lateral, (C) ventral view of the head; (D) pectoral and (E) cloacal regions. Scale bar = 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/242959/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.242960>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Dorsal view of the skull in the genus Leposternon. (A) skull of Leposternon bagual sp. nov. (paratype, FML 11313) with rostral processes of the maxillae and nasals contacting each other on the facial portion of the skull; (B) skull of Leposternon aff. microcephalum (MRT 11984) with rostral processes of the maxillae and nasals not contacting each other on the facial portion of the skull; (C) skull of Leposternon polystegum (ZUFRJ 528) without rostral processes of the maxillae and nasals. Abbreviations: F, frontal; N, nasal; PF, prefrontal; MX, maxilla; NPPM, nasal process of premaxilla; RPM, rostral process of maxilla; RPPM, rostral process of premaxilla." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/242960/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.242961>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Dorsal view of the heads of paratypes of Leposternon bagual sp. nov. (A) FML 11312, (B) FML 11313 and (C) FML 11318. Scale bar = 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/242961/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.242962>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Geographic distribution of Leposternon bagual sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/242962/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

